"<h1>頁面源代碼</h1>\n\n<div class=\"page-source\">\n\t[[iftags -組件]]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[[module CSS]]<br />\n:root {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;--safe: 0,159,107;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;--euclid: 255,211,0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;--keter: 196,2,51;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;--esoteric: 66, 66, 72;<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.contain-class .class-text {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;color: transparent !important;<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.contain-class .class-text::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;content: &quot;{$object}&quot;;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;position: absolute;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;top: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;color: rgba(51,51,51,1) !important;<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.text-part &gt; .main-class::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-right:0;<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.anom-bar-container.esoteric .text-part &gt; .main-class::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: rgba(var(--{$object-color}),1);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-image: url(&quot;{$object-image}&quot;);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;-webkit-filter: invert(0);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;filter: invert(0);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;border-color: rgb(12,12,12);<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.anom-bar-container.esoteric .text-part &gt; .main-class {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: rgb(12,12,12);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background: linear-gradient(30deg,<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rgb(var(--{$esoteric-color}),0.25) 0%,<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rgb(var(--{$esoteric-color}),0.25) 50%,<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rgb(var(--{$object-color}),0.25) 50%,<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rgb(var(--{$object-color}),0.25) 50%<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;)<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.anom-bar-container.esoteric .danger-diamond &gt; .top-icon::before {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: rgb(var(--{$object-color}));<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;background-image: url(&quot;{$object-image}&quot;);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;-webkit-filter: invert(0);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;filter: invert(0);<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.anom-bar-container.esoteric .danger-diamond &gt; .quadrants &gt; .top-quad {<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: rgb(66, 66, 72 ,0.15);<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background-color: rgb(var(--{$object-color}),0.25);<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.anom-bar-container.esoteric .text-part &gt; .main-class &gt; .second-class &gt; .class-text::before {<br />\ncontent: &quot;{$object2}&quot;;<br />\ncolor: #333333;<br />\nfont-size: 0.00;<br />\nfont-size: {$hideObject2};<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n.anom-bar-container.esoteric .text-part &gt; .main-class &gt; .second-class &gt; .class-text {<br />\nfont-size:{$hideObject};<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n[[/iftags]]<br />\n[[iftags +組件]]<br />\n把ACS分類的標題分離開來，以顯示一個機密分級和一個常用的項目等級。<br />\n[[[http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4703|就如同這裡展示的]]]<br />\n<br />\n改編自[[*user Yossipossi]]所撰寫的SCP-4531。<br />\n<br />\n添加以下代碼即可使用：<br />\n&gt; [[include component:acs-peppo-split<br />\n&gt; |object= keter<br />\n&gt; |object-image= http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:anomaly-class-bar/keter-icon.svg<br />\n&gt; |object-color= keter<br />\n&gt; |esoteric-color=機密<br />\n&gt; ]]<br />\n<br />\n如果你希望他只顯示一半的「Safe」或是一半的「Euclid」，請調整「object」、「object-image」以及「object-color」的數值，只需將「 keter」的值更改為「safe」或「 euclid」即可。<br />\n<br />\n+ 查閱頁面原始碼<br />\n[[/iftags]]\n</div>\n"